s restrictions, weighting and clustering,\namong many other features. Companion \\texttt{Python} and \\texttt{R} packages\nwith similar syntax and capabilities are also available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2019 20:59:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Aug 2021 15:03:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 20:23:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-17"}
