nteractions has been\nsuggested as a possible explanation for high $D$ values in these compounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2019 23:09:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Feb 2020 19:41:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-01"}
