ical background) treated in such\nperturbative manner to the corresponding exact solution of GR, where we find\ngood agreement even in the regimes of strong density contrast.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Feb 2019 07:18:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Jul 2019 12:17:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2019 10:29:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-18"}
