ion disk, and, while a very hot low gravity\ndegenerate star dominates the FUV flux, the presence of a steady-state\n(standard) accretion disk cannot be summarily ruled out.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Feb 2019 15:31:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-17"}
